      <p>A field properties overview
         occurs in the <span href='document_type_editor.html'>document type editor</span>.
         In the field properties overview some properties of a field can be set. For example
         every field can be <a href='mandatory_or_optional.xml'>mandatory or optional</a>.
         Other properties are specific for a particular type of field, like the height
         of a text box.
